{"tid":1512839,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[多平台]Rock Man Zero/ZX Legacy Collection 2020年1月21日發售","createTime":"2019-08-28T05:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T21:03:55.000Z","uid":30132,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"973d3558a4b0136a13af61269549a8184dd10081","tid":1512839,"uid":30132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"根據香港 PlayStation Store 提前透露的消息（網頁現已移除），CAPCOM 預定於 2020 年 1 月 21 日在 PS4 ※ 推出集合《洛克人 ZERO（Mega Man Zero）》系列與《洛克人 ZX（Mega Man ZX）》系列共 6 款遊戲的移植合輯《洛克人 ZERO / ZX 傳奇合輯（Mega Man Zero/ZX Legacy Collection）》。<br />\n <br />\n※ 更新：現已確定將會跨 PS4 / Xbox One / Nintendo Switch / PC 推出<br />\n <img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/03/2356a7422805dec56768e7e373161ff5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F03%2F2356a7422805dec56768e7e373161ff5.JPG&h=fa8f5fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9sw9P_UfKkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9sw9P_UfKkM&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2Bm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=5646563c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9sw9P_UfKkM</a><br />\n  《洛克人 ZERO / ZX 傳奇合輯》將收錄 GBA《洛克人 ZERO》系列 1、2、3、4 代及 DS《洛克人 ZX》與《洛克人 ZX 降臨》共 6 款遊戲，能以原本的點陣繪圖畫面或高品質濾鏡畫面來遊玩。收錄可鑑賞原作插畫的「插畫藝廊」與欣賞原作配樂的「音樂播放器」。可自由設定 ZX 系列的雙螢幕配置。提供低難度的「休閒劇情模式」以及可中途存檔的「存檔輔助」功能，讓不擅長動作遊戲的玩家也能安心遊玩體驗故事劇情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/05/2808064ba44b9bb38aed51294f161fh5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F05%2F2808064ba44b9bb38aed51294f161fh5.JPG&h=0a4ba1b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/06/b983ce61ed52c74a6e40228167161fi5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F06%2Fb983ce61ed52c74a6e40228167161fi5.JPG&h=838bd6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/07/6766514ddccc90b862fff37f9d161fj5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F07%2F6766514ddccc90b862fff37f9d161fj5.JPG&h=d8321e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/08/03a52168665b1b44d690ce9459161fk5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F08%2F03a52168665b1b44d690ce9459161fk5.JPG&h=1eb02fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/14/8bee084d278e82ec8a87367266161fq5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F14%2F8bee084d278e82ec8a87367266161fq5.JPG&h=efc27703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  此外，合輯還追加了全新的「Z 追逐模式」，能透過線上排行榜來與其他玩家比拚通關速度。<br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=184871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D184871&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2Bm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=d30981b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=184871</a>"},{"pid":"5e6abc476efe43afb25362dc70a5ee7735413d25","tid":1512839,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2Bm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=8ba9b3a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zA